dc_title_s: Immigration Statistics in the Sessional Papers 1869 - 1882
dc_description_s: Spreadsheet guide to Immigration statistics found in the Sessional Papers of the Canadian Parliament, 1869-1882. Second copy with URLs to Internet Archive, Canadiana.org and other digital copies prepared by: Engstrom, Aurelia; Langrell, Kate; Schmidt,Katherine; Stankovic, Jelena; Szczesniak,Lucy; Tiong, Maggie and added to this study.
